    <description>Auto close duplicate cancelation form requests - same email within 7 days
06/12/25 - PE - Removed cases with the subject &quot;EC Cancellation Request&quot; from being evaluated
06/23/25 - PE - Added EC Cancellation Request cases back to the logic</description>
